        name: LineUp
        Create a object LineUp.
        post: A object LineUp has created.
        Parameters:
        way - is the number who idenfies the tactics. way greater or equal than 1 y way less or equal than 4.
        date - is the date of utilization of line up. date != null y date != "".
        forward - is the number of forwards in the line up. forward greater than 0.
        midfielder - is the number of midfielders in the line up. midfielder greater than 0.
        defender - is the number of defenders in the line up. defender greater than 0.
